          "fill": "#AAAAAA",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Scale basis: 4px base unit. Fine steps +4px linear. Large steps approximately geometric, grid-snapped to nearest 4px. Ratios: 24→32(+8), 32→40(×1.25), 40→48(×1.2), 48→64(×1.333), 64→80(×1.25). Source: Klee Pädagogisches Skizzenbuch, Mondrian Neue Gestaltung, van Doesburg, Gropius, Malevich.",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 10,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
